We used the data to showcase some of the important metrics an Executive Team might want to see. 
It showcase the area in general, with colour codes, to emphasise sales percentages and can be translated in sec.
A sliding bar to the right which can be set to the users wishes and the data will automatically be filtered to meet the users criteria.
The botom half of the report is split into two sections.
Section one show monthly sales by segment.
Section two show sales by catogory.

https://public.tableau.com/app/profile/jo.moore/viz/ExecutiveOverview-Sales_16816267821670/ExecutiveOverview
